e246d8467749ebc3f8cdaaab2f1101","tid":38293,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:52:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b29e530dfc764d9cdfa2dfa90a956caefb57578","tid":38293,"uid":42392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:20:47.000Z","msg":"用火攻"},{"pid":"31520fb1078055e4955c5496bde1a4c92aca2067","tid":38293,"uid":48246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有方法，但唔係人人做到。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係&hellip;断晒佢哋啲糧。即係清潔，唔好畀機會佢哋食到嘢，沒嘢食自然唔會來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0e735b625ee49aa2d935dda4026804c76f5862","tid":38293,"uid":15548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"呢隻曱甴，你見到十隻八隻既話，我都幾肯定你全屋有過百隻係唔同位置。<br />\n想斷尾，搵滅蟲公司上門，幫你用藥水加噴霧，噴霧會谷哂佢地出黎再用藥水就會死哂，幾個鐘之後入返屋就會屍橫遍野。<br />\n記得所有食用工具要徹底洗一次<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企試過。$800-$1200 左右"},{"pid":"61e44d662c5fd3d63e5a33f5ed34a07b3c715a42","tid":38293,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有方法，但唔係人人做到。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係&hellip;断晒佢哋啲糧。即係清潔，唔好畀機會佢哋食到嘢，沒嘢食自然唔會來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8992bfa5ac3a71413e5a49dbb81b78879bcc8215","tid":38293,"uid":48246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有方法，但唔係人人做到。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係&hellip;<span style=\"color: red;\">斷</span>晒佢哋啲糧。即係清潔，唔好畀機會佢哋食到嘢，沒嘢食自然唔會來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已改正。"},{"pid":"96fde7c563e2dd0cdc4a43f73946d26bf7285dbb","tid":38293,"uid":65333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"我屋企都好多"},{"pid":"b42c39b341e1daf762c10529ba2d9d52b26c7e36","tid":38293,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:21:32.000Z","msg":"用一點絕"},{"pid":"462b5a21c47dcf2a6edafdd39ad8f2f3f063b2bf","tid":38293,"uid":61278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"去裕華買藥同艾灸 問服務員就可以 艾灸點著佢放係廚房 好大煙 對人體應該無毒 焗佢半小時"}]}